Defition   : OPT_AUTO_PWD

Defined in : #include <options.h>

Usage      : player->query_option(OPT_AUTO_PWD)

Description: Selects whether the wizards wants to see the pwd (the personal
             working directory) printed when changing directory.

Values     : 0 - Don't see the directory when you change directory.
             1 - See the new working directory after it it changed.
